title: Johor Umno: Teresa Kok also used office as voter address
text:
More 
Pasir Gudang Umno division has questioned why Mengkibol state assemblyperson Tan Hong Pin was critical of Johor Menteri Besar Mohamed Khaled Nordin's voter details and not those from DAP. 
Division assistant secretary Noor Azleen Ambros said the matter should not have arisen given that DAP vice-president Teresa Kok used the address of her service centre to register as a voter.
